Freestanding refrigerator

Freestanding Refrigerators

The integral item to every kitchen, our freestanding fridges are designed with every home in mind. From extra strong glass shelving to support heavy items, to the intelligent curved corners for easy cleaning, AEG larder fridges are created to suit your needs. Every freestanding larder fridge benefits from our Coolmatic function to help items reach the optimum storage temperature so your food stays cool and fresh.
